      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "MORE THAN MERRY (8) has been settling off the speed lately, finishing fourth (30.75) last time in a Grade 5 at Q Parklands. Has ability and can bounce back. ORLANDO BEACH (2) had a tricky draw last time and although midfield in fourth wasn't far away finishing 2 lengths from the winner (19.97). Yet to win out of this box but has been in the placings two times from three starts. Can figure in the finish. UP BEAT (1) has mixed form recently, finishing eighth (20.62) in a Mix 5 at this track latest but did run well two back when in the frame. Safe beginner and drawn well on the inside. Can feature with the right run. JUJU BLUE (3) should bounce back after an unplaced effort here recently.",
